articles.author: Saba Aziz
articles.title: ‘Snowball effect’: Canada’s trucker convoy sparks anti-mandate protests globally - Global News
articles.description: Copycat protests inspired by the so-called “Freedom Convoy” in Ottawa have so far been held in Australia, New Zealand and France, with an American version in the works.
articles.content: The so-called Freedom Convoy protest movement against COVID-19 vaccine mandates that has paralyzed the Canadian capital and spilled over to key Canada-U.S. border crossings has gained global momentum… [+4817 chars]

articles.title: Chinese visitors unlikely to return to Australia in large numbers despite border reopening - ABC News
